      UFVHUAUMUHUIUDUCUE $.
      $( [22-Sep-2002] $)
  $}

  ${
    $d x y A $.  $d x y B $.
    intpr.1 $e |- A e. V $.
    intpr.2 $e |- B e. V $.
    $( The intersection of a pair is the intersection of its members.  Theorem
       71 of [Suppes] p. 42. $)
    intpr $p |- |^| { A , B } = ( A i^i B ) $=
      ( vx vy cpr cint cin cv wcel wi wal wa wceq 19.26 wo visset elpr imbi1i
      jaob bitr albii clel4 anbi12i 3bitr4 elint elin eqriv ) EABGZHZABIZFJZUJK
